<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CIEC Parc-Extension — Entrepreneuriat collectif par les jeunes</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;1,600&family=Lato:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;600&family=Noto+Sans+Gurmukhi:wght@400;600&family=Noto+Sans+Devanagari:wght@400;600&family=Noto+Sans+Bengali:wght@400;600&family=Noto+Naskh+Arabic:wght@400;600&family=Noto+Nastaliq+Urdu:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --ink:#2E2A5E;
    --violet:#7C5CBF;
    --bright:#9B4FD0;
    --lilac:#C9B6E4;
    --wash:#F3EEFA;
    --paper:#FDFCFF;
    --line:#E4DAF2;
    --shadow:rgba(46,42,94,.12);
    --maxw:960px;
  }

  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    margin:0;
    background:var(--paper);
    color:var(--ink);
    font-family:'Lato',system-ui,sans-serif;
    font-size:18px;
    line-height:1.6;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }

  /* ---------- language toggle ---------- */
  .en-only{display:none;}
  body.lang-en .fr-only{display:none;}
  body.lang-en .en-only{display:block;}
  body.lang-en span.en-only{display:inline;}

  .langbar{
    position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;
    display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;align-items:center;gap:10px;
    padding:12px clamp(16px,5vw,48px);
    background:rgba(253,252,255,.9);
    backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .langbar .brandmini{
    margin-right:auto;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700;
    font-size:15px;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--violet);text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .toggle{display:inline-flex;border:2px solid var(--ink);border-radius:100px;overflow:hidden;}
  .toggle button{
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;
    padding:6px 16px;border:0;background:transparent;color:var(--ink);cursor:pointer;
    transition:background .15s,color .15s;
  }
  .toggle button.active{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;}
  .toggle button:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--bright);outline-offset:2px;}

  .wrap{max-width:var(--maxw);margin:0 auto;padding:0 clamp(16px,5vw,48px);}

  /* ---------- hero ---------- */
  .hero{
    position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(120% 90% at 90% -10%, rgba(155,79,208,.16), transparent 55%),
      linear-gradient(180deg,var(--wash),var(--paper));
    padding:clamp(40px,7vw,84px) 0 clamp(32px,5vw,56px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-block;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700;
    font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fff;
    background:var(--violet);padding:7px 16px;border-radius:4px;
    transform:rotate(-1.2deg);box-shadow:2px 3px 0 var(--lilac);
  }
  h1{
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;
    font-size:clamp(34px,6.2vw,60px);line-height:1.02;letter-spacing:-.02em;
    margin:22px 0 0;max-width:16ch;
  }
  h1 .accent{color:var(--bright);}
  .lede{font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,22px);margin:20px 0 0;max-width:56ch;color:#463f77;}
  .datechip{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin-top:26px;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;
    background:#fff;color:var(--ink);padding:10px 18px;border-radius:100px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);box-shadow:0 4px 14px var(--shadow);
  }
  .datechip b{color:var(--bright);}
  .herocta{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;margin-top:26px;}

  .btn{
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;
    text-decoration:none;padding:13px 24px;border-radius:100px;display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;gap:9px;transition:transform .12s,box-shadow .12s;
  }
  .btn:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--bright);outline-offset:3px;}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--bright);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(155,79,208,.35);}
  .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(155,79,208,.45);}
  .btn-ghost{background:#fff;color:var(--ink);border:2px solid var(--ink);}
  .btn-ghost:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);}

  /* ---------- section ---------- */
  section{padding:clamp(44px,6vw,72px) 0;}
  .tape{
    position:relative;display:inline-block;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700;color:#fff;
    font-size:clamp(22px,3.6vw,32px);line-height:1;
    padding:14px 26px;margin:0 0 6px;
    background:linear-gradient(100deg,#9d84c9,#b49ada);
    transform:rotate(-1deg);
    clip-path:polygon(1% 8%,99% 0,100% 86%,2% 100%);
    box-shadow:0 6px 16px var(--shadow);
  }
  .subtitle{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700;color:var(--bright);
    font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,26px);margin:0 0 4px;}
  h2.plain{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,38px);
    letter-spacing:-.01em;margin:0 0 8px;}
  .sectionlede{color:#4a447a;max-width:60ch;margin:14px 0 0;}

  /* ---------- how it works ---------- */
  .steps{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;margin-top:34px;}
  .step{
    background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;
    padding:26px 22px;box-shadow:0 8px 22px var(--shadow);position:relative;
  }
  .step .num{
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:15px;
    width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    background:var(--wash);color:var(--violet);border:2px solid var(--lilac);margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  .step h3{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:19px;margin:0 0 8px;}
  .step p{margin:0;font-size:16px;color:#4a447a;}

  /* ---------- objectives ---------- */
  .obj{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-top:30px;}
  .obj li{
    list-style:none;background:var(--wash);border-radius:14px;padding:22px 20px;
    font-weight:700;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:17px;color:var(--ink);
    border-left:5px solid var(--bright);
  }

  /* ---------- services ---------- */
  .svc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:22px;margin-top:34px;}
  .svc{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 26px;box-shadow:0 8px 22px var(--shadow);}
  .svc h3{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;color:var(--bright);font-size:22px;margin:0 0 4px;}
  .svc .ico{font-size:26px;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .svc ul{margin:14px 0 0;padding:0;list-style:none;}
  .svc li{padding:9px 0 9px 30px;position:relative;border-bottom:1px dashed var(--line);font-weight:600;}
  .svc li:last-child{border-bottom:0;}
  .svc li::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:4px;top:16px;width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--violet);}
  .andmore{margin-top:24px;text-align:center;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;
    color:var(--bright);font-size:20px;letter-spacing:.04em;}

  /* ---------- RECEIPT (signature) ---------- */
  .receiptband{background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--paper),var(--wash));}
  .receipt-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.15fr .85fr;gap:36px;align-items:center;}
  .receipt{
    --perf:14px;
    background:#fff;color:var(--ink);border-radius:6px;position:relative;
    padding:30px 30px 34px;box-shadow:0 14px 34px rgba(46,42,94,.18);
    font-family:'Lato',sans-serif;
  }
  .receipt::before,.receipt::after{
    content:"";position:absolute;left:0;right:0;height:var(--perf);
    background:radial-gradient(circle at 8px 0, transparent 0 7px, #fff 7px) repeat-x;
    background-size:16px 16px;
  }
  .receipt::before{top:calc(-1 * var(--perf) + 1px);
    background:radial-gradient(circle at 8px 16px, transparent 0 7px, #fff 7px) repeat-x;
    background-size:16px 16px;}
  .receipt::after{bottom:calc(-1 * var(--perf) + 1px);}
  .receipt .rhead{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
    border-bottom:2px dashed var(--line);padding-bottom:12px;margin-bottom:16px;}
  .receipt .rtag{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.12em;
    text-transform:uppercase;font-size:12px;color:var(--violet);}
  .receipt .rstamp{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:12px;color:#fff;
    background:var(--bright);padding:5px 11px;border-radius:4px;transform:rotate(3deg);}
  .receipt .rline{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;padding:9px 0;font-size:15px;border-bottom:1px dotted var(--line);}
  .receipt .rline span:last-child{font-weight:700;}
  .receipt .rtotal{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-top:16px;padding-top:14px;border-top:2px solid var(--ink);}
  .receipt .rtotal .lbl{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;}
  .receipt .rtotal .val{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:24px;color:var(--bright);}
  .receipt .rnote{margin-top:12px;font-size:12.5px;color:#6a6398;line-height:1.45;}
  .receipt-copy h2{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,36px);margin:0 0 14px;line-height:1.08;}
  .receipt-copy .hl{color:var(--bright);}
  .receipt-copy p{margin:0 0 14px;color:#463f77;}

  /* ---------- multilingual band ---------- */
  .multi{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;}
  .multi .wrap{padding-top:clamp(44px,6vw,72px);padding-bottom:clamp(44px,6vw,72px);}
  .multi .kicker{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.16em;
    text-transform:uppercase;font-size:13px;color:var(--lilac);}
  .multi h2{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(24px,3.6vw,34px);margin:8px 0 6px;color:#fff;}
  .multi .msub{color:#cfc4ec;max-width:60ch;margin:0 0 30px;}
  .langgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:16px;}
  .langcard{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
    border-radius:16px;padding:20px 22px;
  }
  .langcard .lname{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;
    letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--lilac);margin-bottom:10px;}
  .langcard .ltext{font-size:17px;line-height:1.7;color:#fff;font-family:'Noto Sans',sans-serif;}
  .langcard.rtl .ltext{direction:rtl;text-align:right;}
  .lt-pa{font-family:'Noto Sans Gurmukhi',sans-serif;}
  .lt-hi{font-family:'Noto Sans Devanagari',sans-serif;}
  .lt-bn{font-family:'Noto Sans Bengali',sans-serif;}
  .lt-ar{font-family:'Noto Naskh Arabic',serif;font-size:19px;}
  .lt-ur{font-family:'Noto Nastaliq Urdu',serif;font-size:20px;line-height:2.2;}
  .lt-el,.lt-es{font-family:'Noto Sans',sans-serif;}

  /* ---------- contact ---------- */
  .contact-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:22px;margin-top:34px;}
  .cc{border-radius:20px;padding:30px 28px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:#fff;box-shadow:0 8px 22px var(--shadow);}
  .cc.accent{background:linear-gradient(150deg,var(--violet),var(--bright));color:#fff;border:0;}
  .cc .who{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:21px;margin:0 0 4px;}
  .cc .role{font-size:15px;opacity:.9;margin:0 0 18px;}
  .cc.accent .role{opacity:.92;}
  .cc a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:8px 0;}
  .cc a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
  .cc .cico{width:22px;text-align:center;opacity:.8;}
  .cc .name{font-size:14px;opacity:.85;margin-top:16px;font-style:italic;}

  /* ---------- partners ---------- */
  .partners{background:var(--wash);}
  .partners .wrap{text-align:center;}
  .partners h2{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,28px);margin:0 0 8px;}
  .partners p{color:#4a447a;margin:0 auto 26px;max-width:52ch;}
  .plist{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:10px 12px;max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;}
  .plist span{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:100px;
    padding:9px 18px;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:var(--ink);}

  /* ---------- footer ---------- */
  footer{background:var(--ink);color:#cfc4ec;text-align:center;padding:34px 20px;font-size:14px;}
  footer .fbrand{font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:700;color:#fff;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:6px;}
  footer a{color:var(--lilac);}
  .disclaimer{font-size:12.5px;color:#9b91c9;max-width:60ch;margin:14px auto 0;line-height:1.5;}

  /* ---------- responsive ---------- */
  @media (max-width:760px){
    .steps,.obj,.svc-grid,.receipt-layout,.langgrid,.contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .langbar .brandmini{font-size:12px;}
    .receipt-copy{order:-1;}
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
    *{scroll-behavior:auto;}
    .btn:hover,.btn-primary:hover,.btn-ghost:hover{transform:none;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body class="lang-fr">

<div class="langbar">
  <span class="brandmini">CIEC Parc-Extension</span>
  <div class="toggle" role="group" aria-label="Langue / Language">
    <button id="btn-fr" class="active" onclick="setLang('fr')">FR</button>
    <button id="btn-en" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow fr-only">Coop d'initiation à l'entrepreneuriat collectif</span>
    <span class="eyebrow en-only">Cooperative to launch collective entrepreneurship</span>

    <h1 class="fr-only">Cet été, des <span class="accent">jeunes de Parc-Extension</span> lancent leur coop.</h1>
    <h1 class="en-only">This summer, <span class="accent">Parc-Extension youth</span> run their own co-op.</h1>

    <p class="lede fr-only">La CIEC Parc-Extension réunit des ados de 13 à 17 ans qui offrent des services au quartier — tonte, jardinage, ménage, gardiennage et plus. Vous les engagez, ils apprennent, et vous recevez un reçu fiscal.</p>
    <p class="lede en-only">The Parc-Extension CIEC brings together teens aged 13 to 17 who offer services to the neighbourhood — mowing, gardening, cleaning, babysitting and more. You hire them, they learn, and you get a tax receipt.</p>

    <div class="datechip fr-only">📅 Projet estival&nbsp;: <b>25 juin → 14 août 2026</b></div>
    <div class="datechip en-only">📅 Summer project:&nbsp; <b>June 25 → August 14, 2026</b></div>

    <div class="herocta">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact"><span class="fr-only">Confier un contrat</span><span class="en-only">Hire the youth</span> →</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#recu"><span class="fr-only">Reçu fiscal</span><span class="en-only">Tax receipt</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- WHAT IS A CIEC -->
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="tape fr-only">C'est quoi une CIEC&nbsp;?</span>
    <span class="tape en-only">What is a CIEC?</span>

    <p class="sectionlede fr-only" style="margin-top:22px">Les CIEC — Coopératives d'initiation à l'entrepreneuriat collectif — sont des projets estivaux québécois qui permettent à des ados de 13 à 17 ans de créer et gérer leur propre petite coopérative pour se donner un emploi d'été. Le projet existe depuis 1983&nbsp;: né en Ontario, il a ensuite été adopté au Québec. Cet été, on en compte 45 aux quatre coins de la province.</p>
    <p class="sectionlede en-only" style="margin-top:22px">CIECs — cooperatives to launch collective entrepreneurship — are Quebec summer projects that let teens aged 13 to 17 create and run their own small cooperative to give themselves a summer job. The project has existed since 1983: it started in Ontario before being adopted in Quebec. This summer, 45 CIECs are running across the province.</p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="num">1</div>
        <h3 class="fr-only">Action concrète</h3>
        <h3 class="en-only">Real work</h3>
        <p class="fr-only">Une dizaine à une quinzaine de jeunes du même quartier s'associent pour offrir des services à la communauté&nbsp;: tonte, peinture, jardinage, gardiennage et bien d'autres.</p>
        <p class="en-only">Ten to fifteen youth from the same neighbourhood team up to offer services to the community: mowing, painting, gardening, babysitting and much more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="num">2</div>
        <h3 class="fr-only">Gestion partagée</h3>
        <h3 class="en-only">Shared management</h3>
        <p class="fr-only">Les jeunes forment un conseil d'administration, se partagent les tâches (finance, marketing, ressources humaines) et travaillent ensemble tout en gagnant un salaire.</p>
        <p class="en-only">The youth form a board of directors, split the roles (finance, marketing, human resources) and work together — all while earning a salary.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="num">3</div>
        <h3 class="fr-only">Encadrement</h3>
        <h3 class="en-only">Guidance</h3>
        <p class="fr-only">Le projet est supervisé par deux coordonnateur·rice·s et soutenu par le CJE Centre-Nord.</p>
        <p class="en-only">The project is supervised by two coordinators and supported by CJE Centre-Nord.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OBJECTIVES -->
<section style="padding-top:0">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="subtitle fr-only">Les objectifs</p>
    <p class="subtitle en-only">The goals</p>
    <ul class="obj">
      <li class="fr-only">Développer l'esprit d'équipe, le leadership et l'autonomie.</li>
      <li class="fr-only">S'initier concrètement au marché du travail et aux valeurs de l'entrepreneuriat collectif.</li>
      <li class="fr-only">Vivre une première expérience de travail enrichissante.</li>
      <li class="en-only">Build teamwork, leadership and independence.</li>
      <li class="en-only">Get a hands-on introduction to the job market and the values of collective entrepreneurship.</li>
      <li class="en-only">Gain a first, rewarding work experience.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES -->
